title: Yvette Nicole Brown / Diabetes & Caregiving
description: Sean suffers from Tendonitis and Carpal Tunnel. Yvette charms us with her nerd knowledge (guess who wins the Dr. Wali's Hall of Fame?) and shares her experience with Diabetes. We also shine a light on caregiving.
author: info@hazymills.com (Hazy Mills Network)
